Utility for determining if an object is of specific type.

The functions have in common, that they take all one positional argument and return a boolean value (object => bool).

vizasm.model.ModelUtil.destination_not_initialized(val)[source]¶

Check if the destination of an objc_msgSend is not initialized (has 0 as value). Do not check for 0 as int! Because an zero destination will be wrapped inside a certain class indicating a not initialized variable/destination
